<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10369768>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Larnaca (Larnaca) nigrifrons Pang, Zhang & Bian, 2023. Male: A. head in frontal view; B–C. head and pronotum: B. dorsal view, C. lateral view; D. right tegmen in lateral view; E. second and third abdominal tergites in lateral view; F. hind legs in lateral view; G–L. apex of abdomen: G. dorsal view, H. lateral view, I. apico-ventral view, J. apical view, K. ventro-lateral view, L. ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10369768/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10369772>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Larnaca (Larnaca) nigrifrons Pang, Zhang & Bian, 2023. Female: A–B. head: A. in frontal view, B. frontal and lateral view; C–E. head and pronotum: C. dorsal and slightly lateral view, D. dorsal view, E. lateral view; F. left wings in lateral view; G. second and third abdominal tergites in lateral view; H. apex of abdomen in lateral view; I. left hind leg in external view; J. seventh abdominal sternite and subgenital plate in ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10369772/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

